data.description: Brick range with a finished basement. Very unique home with tons of storage space. 4 bedrooms, 2 baths plus a bath in garage as well. Hardwood floors and new carpet on the main floor. The basement has a finished rec room with a fireplace and great for entertaining. The potential and possiblities are endless!
